# 正常削除（pk 明示）
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/delete-item/Consignors/a42bf96f-1a69-4530-9575-d1e5181f8c86/pk-consignors
Accept: application/json

###

# 404（存在しない ID）
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/delete-item/Consignors/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

# 400（無効な UUID）
DELETE http://localhost:7071/api/delete-item/Consignors/not-a-uuid
Accept: application/json

